Instructions for translators:
The messages in this file use the ICU Message Format Syntax. Placeholders for arguments are surrounded by curly braces: {name, type, style}. The name, type, and style of the arguments must not be translated. Sub-messages for plural and select arguments in nested curly braces do need to be translated: {gender, select, male {Men} female {Women} other {Other}}. Single quotes are used to escape special characters.
For more information see the following resources:
* ICU User Guide: http://userguide.icu-project.org/formatparse/messages
* Related Java API: http://icu-project.org/apiref/icu4j/com/ibm/icu/text/MessageFormat.html
* Related PHP API: http://php.net/manual/en/class.messageformatter.php
